This chat can only be accessed by users with the "Nootropic Enthusiast" role. "Nootropic Enthusiast" is given to those that know their nootropics and have had plenty of experience with nootropic study & use. 

The idea behind this role is to keep the number of members low to increase dicussion quality. Over time, the members of this group will decide or vote upon which members to include or exclude based upon interactions in chat, voice, and on the subreddit.

 Moderators should not comment unless it is to address a rule violation or to add/remove a member from the group.
